Section 8
	Lecture 49: JPA DAO(Data Access Object) Service

1. Create new ProductServiceJpaDaoImpl.java in the services package and implements methods.
2. Declare service component using the @Service annotation in the ProductServiceJpaDaoImpl class
3. Declare profile configuration using the @Profile annotation in the ProductServiceJpaDaoImpl class
4. Declare profile map using the @Profile annotation in the ProductServiceImpl class
5. Setup profile configuration in the application.properties to active
6. Setup entity manager factory in the ProductServiceJpaDaoImpl.java (to use Thread Safe)
7. Create Setter for the entity manager factory
8. Add @PersistenceUnit JPA annotation (Note: It's not spring annotation) to injecting entity manager factory.
9. Declare and implements listAll() method ProductServiceJpaDaoImpl.java
 9.1 Declare Entity Manager
 9.2 Declare return using the declared entity manager
10. Declare and implements getById() method ProductServiceJpaDaoImpl.java

11. Declare and implements saveOrUpdate() method ProductServiceJpaDaoImpl.java

12. Declare and implements delete() method ProductServiceJpaDaoImpl.java

13. Add version property in the productform.html

14. Run and Test

